body:
Really curious indeed, I recognize this as one of my first doujinshis I had read, almost 8 years ago, and read the first part it a few times already, but was just today when I remembered again, looked for it and find the entire story, read it, manage to fap two times, but when the queen showed up the interest went to the plot.
That ending was just simple, but at the same time epic.
The alice series is pretty underrated all things considered.
What a reality check, the ending was very good.
